{"tid":1764684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日無出去嘅立即入曬黎做依樣野。","createTime":"2019-12-01T09:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T10:55:51.000Z","uid":41292,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7de76ee0d5b1ff115b9bb10d4967cd3ff8f5c061","tid":1764684,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:44:19.000Z","msg":"識外語就去外語嘅討論區，唔識嘅就係Twitter/Reddit推今日嘅事。<br />\n1.日頭開強光電筒照向群眾，具有強烈嘅攻擊意圖。<br />\n2.和平嘅示威係人群之間放催淚彈意圖製造多次碧街慘劇。<br />\n3.推跪地女仔落地，證明佢地係單純敵視香港人以及情緒化問題嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n跟住了解下佢地嘅公投制度，請求佢地定下法案幫助香港。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我知好多時做左都無用，但比起睇Live上黎鳩up，你向外宣傳會有作用好多。"},{"pid":"04276750cd304aae4d72609f2fc36d099536fdd6","tid":1764684,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"外媒記者有報<br />\n今日警察向和平示威者噴胡椒tg<br />\n快啲推上國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B6Zg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=9c92fdec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"0f058476d5bfb34d1815f1276ea5c224745190a1","tid":1764684,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:55:01.000Z","msg":"pushhh"},{"pid":"4a873f281fcf7b5a8aebc80d40eb4d6f2206ee58","tid":1764684,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:57:39.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n無出去就唔好再嬲再乜野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港個個人都嬲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地要做嘅野唔係同人請你有幾嬲<br />\n<br />\n係要比外國人知點解你會嬲，同埋佢地應該點幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b64515321c9f560ecc8169b3eebf4c6b3677e50","tid":1764684,"uid":104645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"109e7c372236709dd9ebe92d4356067ec59acacc","tid":1764684,"uid":200663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:58:53.000Z","msg":"出唔到去 可以做文宣 鍵戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f6e175541be856f4ab19f2639363cb4eea5e48","tid":1764684,"uid":176996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:59:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cdd3b123598abcf897ee6b040a858a8bb908b560","tid":1764684,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:07:04.000Z","msg":"今日開始<br />\nIG story 要從好嬲<br />\n變成同外國宣傳嘅方法！<br />\n<br />\n用曬我地嘅知識力量，<br />\n去用所有嘅方法去幫香港人。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每個人做到嘅嘢都唔同</span><br />\n<br />\n娛樂迷好似韓迷日迷用盡你嘅樂迷圈子發放資料，<br />\n藝術方面嘅盡全力係自己作品到帶出香港嘅情況。<br />\n識外語嘅就盡力了解當地嘅立法程序，到外國嘅討論區請求支援。<br />\n<br />\n美國、荷蘭、義大利、英國同埋澳洲都開始有行動，<br />\n各位要盡自己所有嘅專長、技能同埋影響力去宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3b8c36bf6ab0b9ed12c2fb245a9bfe9d51bccd","tid":1764684,"uid":13318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:23:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7001eff04a5a494135501e96d56a3f611d4385aa","tid":1764684,"uid":233338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:25:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4009445fe3efab1b3c6d6b5b5b23f1b1e0544e6f","tid":1764684,"uid":263905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:39:44.000Z","msg":"‪#HKPoliceTerrorists #HKPoliceBrutality #chinazi<br />\n推"},{"pid":"1639c49624992efc5717e02b770e82d8baa1c9b4","tid":1764684,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"推呀"}]}